# Workflow Modes & Context Tags

- Main modes: [discuss], [meta], [code], [debug], [docs], [test]
- Combined modes: [code][debug], [discuss][meta], [docs][meta]
- Best practices: always specify the mode at the start of a session or task, switch modes as the work phase changes, use modes to filter tasks, logs, insights, the AI must update llm_context and attention_marker when switching modes, always log mode switches for automation and analysis. 